    <briefdescription>
<para>Reacts to HealthDepletedEvents and despawns or deactivates entities. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Reads HealthDepletedEvents from the phase bus. For each affected entity, the system inspects the HealthComponent&apos;s <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1health_1_1types_1a9743835a1d9bdeab71ea28ed3603b3fd" kindref="member">HealthDepletedBehavior</ref> flags:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>If Despawn is set and the entity has a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1spawn_1_1components_1_1SpawnedByProfileComponent" kindref="compound">SpawnedByProfileComponent</ref>, a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1spawn_1_1commands_1_1DespawnCommand" kindref="compound">DespawnCommand</ref> is enqueued.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Otherwise the entity is deactivated. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
